p.k: The Lonely Haunts Club 2: Doll Island In order to prove their bravery, Vic & Val head to a haunted island to retrieve a special doll, but Charlene and Pineapple are intent on getting it first.
p.d: Victor and Valentino is a supernatural adventure comedy about two half-brothers who spend a summer with their grandma in a place called Monte Macabre, a small and mysterious town.
